        "TileImage": "$($repository 3a73412e-81e0-42a1-a9b5-d59501e04ae2).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47.\rYour targets are the diamond couriers of Xander Haverfoek, who was recently eliminated by you. Our client believes that eliminating Xander alone will not weaken the flow of future diamonds to Hugo Strenberg, so it is necessary to eliminate the remaining members of the network. Hurry up, 47, as we have learned that Lucas Thorvaldsson has already changed his passport information and will soon leave the country.\rThe clock is ticking, 47. Good luck.",
